{
  "id": "69f58d766545772913754bae",
  "title": "花友フェスタ初参戦",
  "created": 1777700216,
  "updated": 1777779080,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f58d766545772913754bae",
      "text": "花友フェスタ初参戦",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656d7",
      "text": "from [2026/04/29]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656d8",
      "text": "   花友フェスタ初参戦",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656d9",
      "text": "[onuma.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656da",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/975588a8c84e5a8ce59300218d174a1c]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656db",
      "text": "  初参戦",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656dc",
      "text": "  店員さんがこれお気に入りなんですーって言ってて、絶対枯らさないと誓った",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656dd",
      "text": "   情熱が伝わってきた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656de",
      "text": "  トークショーってこんな感じなんだなあ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656df",
      "text": "   メインの人がしゃべるんじゃなくて、メインの人が呼んだ人たちがしゃべっている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656e0",
      "text": "   メインの人にしか興味がないからあまり楽しめないかも",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656e1",
      "text": "   かなり離席している人も多い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656e2",
      "text": "  知らん世界だ[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656e3",
      "text": "  \t[ガーデニング]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656e4",
      "text": "  \t楽しいですよ[onuma.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656e5",
      "text": "   \t自分でもなんでこんなに好きなのかは良くわからない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656e6",
      "text": "   \t遺伝子に刻み込まれたなにかを感じる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656e7",
      "text": " ガーデニングはいろいろトラブルもあるからストレスもあるのだが",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656e8",
      "text": "  いろんな要素が関わって完全に自分の掌下におけないところが中毒性の元なのかも",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656e9",
      "text": "   天候とか、その年の害虫の発生具合とか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656ea",
      "text": "  ギャンブルみたいな、ほどよい成功体験と失敗体験のバランスなのか？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58d7700000000000656eb",
      "text": "   ほどよいというのは中毒性を示すのにほどよいの意",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777700216,
      "updated": 1777700216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5cf070000000000a0e85f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1777716999,
      "updated": 1777716999
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5cf080000000000a0e860",
      "text": "　花友フェスタとてもよかった",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1777717000,
      "updated": 1777717042
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5cf320000000000a0e861",
      "text": "\t\tまず通路がとても広く確保されており、かなり歩きやすかった",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1777717042,
      "updated": 1777717096
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5cf690000000000a0e862",
      "text": "\t\t大きな戦利品を台車やコロコロするやつ（名前を知らん、スーツケースみたいに転がすやつ）する人も結構いた",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1777717097,
      "updated": 1777717346
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5cfbe0000000000a0e863",
      "text": "\t\t体感的に、多肉植物がかなり多め",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1777717182,
      "updated": 1777717201
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5cfd60000000000a0e864",
      "text": "\t\t\t主催者が多肉の人らしい",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1777717206,
      "updated": 1777717216
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5ce8b0000000000a0e856",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1777716875,
      "updated": 1777716875
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5ce8b0000000000a0e857",
      "text": "　戦利品その１：ジュエルオーキッド",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1777716875,
      "updated": 1777716901
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5ceb50000000000a0e85b",
      "text": "　\t[https://gyazo.com/07bdc2e97fd94d17c3b6e1cc78aba074]",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1777716917,
      "updated": 1777716953
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5d535000000000013344b",
      "text": " 　\tあまりにも整っていてかつ珍妙な模様（更に写真のとり方も綺麗）なので名前も相まって造り物のように見えるが自然の植物なのだろう[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777718582,
      "updated": 1777718744
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5d606000000000013344c",
      "text": " 　\t\t[綺麗すぎる]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777718791,
      "updated": 1777718794
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5d6c00000000000dd9f25",
      "text": " 　\t\t自分もはじめて見たとき目を疑った[onuma.icon]",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1777718976,
      "updated": 1777719049
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5d6d20000000000dd9f26",
      "text": "  　\t\t写真で黄色く見えてる葉脈がラメのように金属光沢を持っててすごく綺麗",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1777718994,
      "updated": 1777719029
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5d7540000000000dd5896",
      "text": "　\t\t粒々のように見えているのは水滴",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1777719124,
      "updated": 1777719135
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5d75f0000000000dd5897",
      "text": " 　\t\t湿ったところが好きな植物",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1777719135,
      "updated": 1777719209
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5ced90000000000a0e85c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1777716953,
      "updated": 1777716953
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5ce9c0000000000a0e859",
      "text": "　戦利品その２：山紅葉のミニ盆栽",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1777716892,
      "updated": 1777716916
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5ceee0000000000a0e85d",
      "text": "　\t[https://gyazo.com/936d666f0f12de212a3edbc2aa3c147f]",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1777716974,
      "updated": 1777779080
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6c18800000000001d45b4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1777779080,
      "updated": 1777779080
    },
    {
